DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: What do you mean you were a puppet?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: What do you mean you were a puppet?

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Why aren't you like the other goblins?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Why aren't you like the other goblins?

Message.SourceString: [TEMP] You are carrying to much for me to give you your reward!
Message.LocalizedString: [TEMP] You are carrying to much for me to give you your reward!

Message.SourceString: There is nothing there but dust.
Message.LocalizedString: There is nothing there but dust.

Message.SourceString: I sensed something up there by the ruin over there, beneath this outlook, and south toward the guild.
Message.LocalizedString: I sensed something up there by the ruin over there, beneath this outlook, and south toward the guild.

Message.SourceString: There is nothing there but dust.
Message.LocalizedString: There is nothing there but dust.

Message.SourceString: You discover a strange amulet in the reliquary, but your inventory is too full to pick it up right now.
Message.LocalizedString: You discover a strange amulet in the reliquary, but your inventory is too full to pick it up right now.

Message.SourceString: If you'd got here sooner, I'd help you find this lot's stuff. But that weird garou-beastmen nutjob got here first. Weird fella, lives in a cave in the swamp.
Message.LocalizedString: If you'd got here sooner, I'd help you find this lot's stuff. But that weird garou-beastmen nutjob got here first. Weird fella, lives in a cave in the swamp.

Message.SourceString: How's I know? I smells it on ya mate, you stinky of theivery. Probably nicked something shiny from the other tribe.
Message.LocalizedString: How's I know? I smells it on ya mate, you stinky of theivery. Probably nicked something shiny from the other tribe.

Message.SourceString: How's the investigation going? Found anything yet?
Message.LocalizedString: How's the investigation going? Found anything yet?

Message.SourceString: You lookin to steal stuff? Well's your a bit too late.
Message.LocalizedString: You lookin to steal stuff? Well's your a bit too late.

Message.SourceString: Yeah, nick their stuff! That'll teach 'em.
Message.LocalizedString: Yeah, nick their stuff! That'll teach 'em.

Message.SourceString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?
Message.LocalizedString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?

Message.SourceString: Ah, you're alright human. Not as ugly on the inside as ya is on the outside.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, you're alright human. Not as ugly on the inside as ya is on the outside.

Message.SourceString: Go, on, do me a solid and bring me a nice steak? I'll tell ya where they hides their treasure if you do.
Message.LocalizedString: Go, on, do me a solid and bring me a nice steak? I'll tell ya where they hides their treasure if you do.

Message.SourceString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?
Message.LocalizedString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?

Message.SourceString: Well if you're gonna interrupt me, why not grab me some food, eh? Cos, like, I'm proper starvin right now.
Message.LocalizedString: Well if you're gonna interrupt me, why not grab me some food, eh? Cos, like, I'm proper starvin right now.

Message.SourceString: Go, on, do me a solid and bring me a nice steak? I'll tell ya where they hides their treasure if you do.
Message.LocalizedString: Go, on, do me a solid and bring me a nice steak? I'll tell ya where they hides their treasure if you do.

Message.SourceString: Wait, I smell steak on ya? If you hand it over I'll tell you where they hide their secret stuff.
Message.LocalizedString: Wait, I smell steak on ya? If you hand it over I'll tell you where they hide their secret stuff.

Message.SourceString: Wait, I smell steak on ya? If you hand it over I'll tell you where they hide their secret stuff.
Message.LocalizedString: Wait, I smell steak on ya? If you hand it over I'll tell you where they hide their secret stuff.

Message.SourceString: Well, fine! No steak, no secrets! See if I care.
Message.LocalizedString: Well, fine! No steak, no secrets! See if I care.

Message.SourceString: If you want to get yer hand on this lot's stuff, you'll want to look behind them barrels and crates. Not good at hiding things this lot.
Message.LocalizedString: If you want to get yer hand on this lot's stuff, you'll want to look behind them barrels and crates. Not good at hiding things this lot.

Message.SourceString: How's I know? I smells it on ya mate, you stinky of theivery. Probably nicked something shiny from the other tribe.
Message.LocalizedString: How's I know? I smells it on ya mate, you stinky of theivery. Probably nicked something shiny from the other tribe.

Message.SourceString: If you'd got here sooner, I'd help you find this lot's stuff. But that weird garou-beastmen nutjob got here first. Weird fella, lives in a cave in the swamp.
Message.LocalizedString: If you'd got here sooner, I'd help you find this lot's stuff. But that weird garou-beastmen nutjob got here first. Weird fella, lives in a cave in the swamp.

Message.SourceString: I died, got resurrected and my soul was marked by his claim. I had no choice in the matter.
Message.LocalizedString: I died, got resurrected and my soul was marked by his claim. I had no choice in the matter.

Message.SourceString: The war god hated anything that wasn't combat. So where the surface goblins stagnated, we cave goblins thrived.
Message.LocalizedString: The war god hated anything that wasn't combat. So where the surface goblins stagnated, we cave goblins thrived.

Message.SourceString: He came to our world, Gielinor, and ignited war. Laughing all the while at the carnage.
Message.LocalizedString: He came to our world, Gielinor, and ignited war. Laughing all the while at the carnage.

Message.SourceString: I nearly became something awful, but a friend helped me resist Bandos and put a stop to his scheme.
Message.LocalizedString: I nearly became something awful, but a friend helped me resist Bandos and put a stop to his scheme.

Message.SourceString: But... Bandos' mark still dug deep into my being and when he died... well, so did I.
Message.LocalizedString: But... Bandos' mark still dug deep into my being and when he died... well, so did I.

Message.SourceString: I mean, I got better, but still, these things haunt you.
Message.LocalizedString: I mean, I got better, but still, these things haunt you.

Message.SourceString: He was banished, like all the gods, with Guthix's edicts. Then returned after Guthix died to immediately pick a fight.
Message.LocalizedString: He was banished, like all the gods, with Guthix's edicts. Then returned after Guthix died to immediately pick a fight.

Message.SourceString: He challenged the god of justice, Armadyl, and the two raced to build a god-killing weapon. Armadyl finished his first.
Message.LocalizedString: He challenged the god of justice, Armadyl, and the two raced to build a god-killing weapon. Armadyl finished his first.

Message.SourceString: Armadyl slew Bandos, leaving the universe in a better state. I do not regret his passing. Gielinor is better for it.
Message.LocalizedString: Armadyl slew Bandos, leaving the universe in a better state. I do not regret his passing. Gielinor is better for it.

Message.SourceString: We chose peace. Peace and understanding, and now cave goblin society is wonderfully advanced.
Message.LocalizedString: We chose peace. Peace and understanding, and now cave goblin society is wonderfully advanced.

Message.SourceString: I look at goblins and see what we were and sometimes I'd like them to see who they *could* be.
Message.LocalizedString: I look at goblins and see what we were and sometimes I'd like them to see who they *could* be.

Message.SourceString: Armadyl slew Bandos, leaving the universe in a better state. I do not regret his passing. Gielinor is better for it.
Message.LocalizedString: Armadyl slew Bandos, leaving the universe in a better state. I do not regret his passing. Gielinor is better for it.

Message.SourceString: Take this, a little something for your trouble. A reminder that we're all masters of our own fate.
Message.LocalizedString: Take this, a little something for your trouble. A reminder that we're all masters of our own fate.

Message.SourceString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?
Message.LocalizedString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?

Message.SourceString: Do you feel it too? Prophecy. A god's backup plan, waiting for a host to sink its tendrils into.
Message.LocalizedString: Do you feel it too? Prophecy. A god's backup plan, waiting for a host to sink its tendrils into.

Message.SourceString: I sensed something up there by the ruin over there, beneath this outlook, and south toward the guild.
Message.LocalizedString: I sensed something up there by the ruin over there, beneath this outlook, and south toward the guild.

Message.SourceString: Something dangerous is hidden out here. It's sealed for now, probably in an amulet or something but we need to find it. By we, I mean you.
Message.LocalizedString: Something dangerous is hidden out here. It's sealed for now, probably in an amulet or something but we need to find it. By we, I mean you.

Message.SourceString: I'm vulnerable to prophecy, I was Bandos' puppet for a while and I can't risk that again. Never again.
Message.LocalizedString: I'm vulnerable to prophecy, I was Bandos' puppet for a while and I can't risk that again. Never again.

Message.SourceString: Bandos was a war god. The Big High War God, in the parlance of my people. He delighted in conflict, battle and bloodshed.
Message.LocalizedString: Bandos was a war god. The Big High War God, in the parlance of my people. He delighted in conflict, battle and bloodshed.

Message.SourceString: Yeah, nick their stuff! That'll teach 'em.
Message.LocalizedString: Yeah, nick their stuff! That'll teach 'em.

Message.SourceString: Truth is, I'm a cave goblin -- a different tribe. We escaped Bandos' efforts in the god wars and forged a life of our own.
Message.LocalizedString: Truth is, I'm a cave goblin -- a different tribe. We escaped Bandos' efforts in the god wars and forged a life of our own.

Message.SourceString: I'm vulnerable to prophecy, I was Bandos' puppet for a while and I can't risk that again. Never again.

Message.LocalizedString: There is nothing there but dust.

Message.SourceString: The reliquary has already been opened and the contents removed. There are claw marks along the outside and traces of stagnant water and mud within. Perhaps someone nearby saw something.

Message.SourceString: Whatever that druid was trying to do, I'm glad you stopped it. It would definitely not have ended well.
Message.LocalizedString: Whatever that druid was trying to do, I'm glad you stopped it. It would definitely not have ended well.

Message.SourceString: A prophecy is like a parasite, burrowing into your soul. Twisting your choices to get its own way.
Message.LocalizedString: A prophecy is like a parasite, burrowing into your soul. Twisting your choices to get its own way.

Message.SourceString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?
Message.LocalizedString: What you want? Can't you see I'm busy plotting me escape?

Message.SourceString: We should all forge our own paths, don't you think?
Message.LocalizedString: We should all forge our own paths, don't you think?

Message.SourceString: Here, I'll take those from you. I know how to dispose of prophecies.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, I'll take those from you. I know how to dispose of prophecies.

Message.SourceString: You did it! I knew you could!
Message.LocalizedString: You did it! I knew you could!

Message.LocalizedString: Careful, this whole area is full of goblins and not the nice kind like me. What brings you all the way out here?

Message.SourceString: Why would someone take it? Don't they need both pieces for the prophecy... unless...

Message.SourceString: I've been tracking a strange presence in the swamps, not far from the northeast ruins. You need to find the other piece, and quickly. There might be darker powers at work.
Message.LocalizedString: I've been tracking a strange presence in the swamps, not far from the northeast ruins. You need to find the other piece, and quickly. There might be darker powers at work.

Message.SourceString: Oh, wait, that amulet, that's the source of the uncomfortable feeling I felt.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, wait, that amulet, that's the source of the uncomfortable feeling I felt.

Message.SourceString: It's a prophecy alright, one of Bandos' safeguards. Although, since he's dead, who else might use it?
Message.LocalizedString: It's a prophecy alright, one of Bandos' safeguards. Although, since he's dead, who else might use it?

Message.SourceString: It's only half of the magic though. We need to find both pieces.
Message.LocalizedString: It's only half of the magic though. We need to find both pieces.

Message.SourceString: I felt the other presence near the ruin to the northeast.
Message.LocalizedString: I felt the other presence near the ruin to the northeast.

Message.SourceString: It's actually quite fascinating being here, without a prophecy to worry about.
Message.LocalizedString: It's actually quite fascinating being here, without a prophecy to worry about.

Message.SourceString: The goblins round here are so different from those back home, they don't even worship Bandos.
Message.LocalizedString: The goblins round here are so different from those back home, they don't even worship Bandos.

Message.SourceString: They follow the dragons instead, which is really interesting. I wonder if it changes how their society lives?
Message.LocalizedString: They follow the dragons instead, which is really interesting. I wonder if it changes how their society lives?

Message.SourceString: Do you think they'd object to me taking notes of their rituals? They probably would, right? Dagnammit.
Message.LocalizedString: Do you think they'd object to me taking notes of their rituals? They probably would, right? Dagnammit.

Message.SourceString: There are always darker powers. There are things worse than gods... older than the gods.
Message.LocalizedString: There are always darker powers. There are things worse than gods... older than the gods.

Message.SourceString: Let's just stop this nonsense before we meet them.
Message.LocalizedString: Let's just stop this nonsense before we meet them.
